OL,4,Cto kill a nurse with scissors
OL,6,FA hospital patient who attacked a
OL,7,Fnurse with a pair of scissors has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty of attempted murder.
OL,10,FRomon Haque, 38, viciously stabbed 57-
OL,11,Fyear-old Acheema Cherian in an
OL,12,Funprovoked attack at the Royal Oldham
OL,13,FHospital on 11 January which left her
OL,14,Fin intensive care.
OL,16,FHaque had asked her for medication at
OL,17,Faround 10.35pm, before lunging at her
OL,18,Fbecause she was with another patient,
OL,19,FManchester Minshull Street Crown Court
OL,20,Fwas told.
