OL,4,Cto kill a nurse with scissors
OL,6,FHe then went to the door of the bay
OL,7,Fand struck the nurse from behind with
OL,8,Fscissors. As she turned to try and
OL,9,Fdefend herself, she was stabbed in the
OL,10,Fforehead, wrist and the palm of her
OL,11,Fhand.
OL,13,FProsecuting, Nicholas Rhodes KC, said
OL,14,FHaque "came across a pair of sharp
OL,15,Fpointed hospital scissors which he
OL,16,Fpicked up and secreted on his person".
OL,18,FHe said: "The scissors are hospital
OL,19,Fissue, normally kept in a locked
OL,20,Fsecure room on the unit, away from
OL,21,Fpatients."
