OL,6,FThe attack only stopped when another
OL,7,Fmember of staff managed to restrain
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,FMs Cherian's injuries meant she
OL,11,Fremained in intensive care overnight.
OL,13,FHaque had been admitted three days
OL,14,Fearlier for a mental health
OL,15,Fassessment, but it was later concluded
OL,16,Fhis symptoms were caused by drug and
OL,17,Falcohol withdrawal.
