OL,6,FHaque was arrested by police and made
OL,7,Fno comment in his police interview,
OL,8,Fother than to tell officers he hears
OL,9,Fvoices.
OL,11,FAfter his appearance at court, Haque
OL,12,Fwas assessed and deemed fit to stand
OL,13,Ftrial by two psychiatrists.
OL,15,FOn 7 July 2025, he pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fpossession of a bladed article but not
OL,17,Fguilty to attempted murder.
