OL,6,FHe accepted that he had attacked the
OL,7,Fnurse and caused serious injuries but
OL,8,Fclaimed that he had no intention to
OL,9,Fkill her.
OL,11,FHaque was found guilty of attempted
OL,12,Fmurder on 18 July 2025.
OL,14,FSenior Crown Prosecutor Claire Aitken
OL,15,Fsaid: "Romon Haque's savage attack of
OL,16,Fa nurse who was carrying out her
OL,17,Fduties, was truly appalling.
